# Environment Setup
- This project uses uv for Python environment management
- The PyMAPDL environment is located at: `.PyMAPDL/`
- To activate the environment: `& ".PyMAPDL/Scripts/Activate.ps1"` (PowerShell)
- To run Python scripts: `& ".PyMAPDL/Scripts/python.exe" script.py`

# Style
- Do not create any test file during conversation
- Python 3.12
- Avoid reintroducing stateful globals
